section.featuresSlider
  .featuresSlider__content
    h2.subPage__title.featuresSlider__title Key Features
    .featuresSlider__btns
      button.featuresSlider-btn.featuresSlider-btn_left
        | left
        +icon('arrow')
      button.featuresSlider-btn.featuresSlider-btn_right
        | Right
        +icon('arrow')
  .swiper.featuresSlider-swiper
    ul.featuresSlider-list.swiper-wrapper
      li.featuresSlider-list__item.swiper-slide
        .featuresSlider-list__content
          span.featuresSlider-list__title Decentralized execution network
          span.featuresSlider-list__text EigenLayer and Symbiotic-secured operators execute your transactions with cryptographic consensus and slashing guarantees. No centralized points of failure or operator risk.
      li.featuresSlider-list__item.swiper-slide
        .featuresSlider-list__content
          span.featuresSlider-list__title Economic Guarantees &amp; Slashing
          span.featuresSlider-list__text Get financial guarantees on execution with economic alignment: if the network under-delivers, penalties apply. Your most critical transactions stay protected.
      li.featuresSlider-list__item.swiper-slide
        .featuresSlider-list__content
          span.featuresSlider-list__title Advanced Trigger System
          span.featuresSlider-list__text Configure complex conditions combining time-based schedules, price oracles, on-chain events, and custom logic. Support for cron expressions, block-based timing, and cross-chain coordination.
      li.featuresSlider-list__item.swiper-slide
        .featuresSlider-list__content
          span.featuresSlider-list__title Multi-Chain Orchestration
          span.featuresSlider-list__text Execute coordinated workflows across multiple EVM chains with atomic guarantees. Bridge assets, synchronize states, and manage cross-chain positions seamlessly.
      li.featuresSlider-list__item.swiper-slide
        .featuresSlider-list__content
          span.featuresSlider-list__title Non-Custodial &amp; AA-Native
          span.featuresSlider-list__text Keep assets in your custody. Leverage Account Abstraction modules (smart sessions, paymasters) to batch, authorize, and gas-abstract recurring operations.
